      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving German engineering, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine. The powerplant maintains impeccable compression across all cylinders, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal valve timing. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded rod bearings, addressing the chassis's known longitudinal stress points. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential that ensures linear power delivery. Finished with a pristine undercarriage and factory-spec suspension geometry, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience with zero mechanical compromise. Full service documentation confirms its status as a collector-grade asset.",
